# List Constructor Syntax

Rewrite rule:

- _T[…]_ ⟹ _T([…])_

Uppercase unary functions may elide application parenthesis when applied to lists, vectors, matrices and volumes.

At `List Syntax`:

```
>>> Set[]
Set([])

>>> Set[1, 2, 3]
Set([1, 2, 3])
```

At `Vector Syntax`:

```
>>> Set[1 2 3]
Set([1 2 3])
```

